    "direction": null,
    "content": "<p>The correct order of relative stability of the given conformers of n-butane is</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/1l2pd7eu4/d098c619-0d0f-4c6c-8e43-8967ca786d90/49c141c0-ca71-11ec-a871-536c573c5df4/file-1l2pd7eu5.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/1l2pd7eu4/d098c619-0d0f-4c6c-8e43-8967ca786d90/49c141c0-ca71-11ec-a871-536c573c5df4/file-1l2pd7eu5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0px auto;max-height:40vh\" alt=\"WB JEE 2022 Chemistry - Isomerism Question 7 English\"></p>",
